## Comment Style

Comments should sound human and natural. Avoid:
- AI-sounding language
- Em dashes
- Overly formal or corporate tone

Good: "Done. All 41 sites loaded with capacity and usage data. Cross-checked against Envizi source."
Bad: "This task has been completed — all 41 Phase 1 sites have been successfully loaded..."

## Bulk Operations

When updating multiple items, run commands in parallel where possible. After each batch, confirm success by checking the returned state field in the response.
